                  href="Section_1517_208_T48_601315113.dita#Section_1517_208_T48_601315113">1517.208</xref>(d), insert this contract clause in cost-reimbursement type term form contracts when applicable. If only one option period is used, enter “NA” in the proper places of the clause. If more than two option periods apply, modify the clause accordingly.
</p>
